{"tid":408396,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"黃埔花園滅蟲工失足　天台飛墮毀棚慘死","createTime":"2017-09-21T07:42:27.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-21T10:14:25.000Z","uid":75969,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"e5d78556cdace6e51a8de9e252dc69ed4fc807b4","tid":408396,"uid":75969,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-21T07:42:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20170921/photo/bkn-20170921111104481-0921_00822_001_01p.jpg?20170921152603\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20170921%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20170921111104481-0921_00822_001_01p.jpg%3F20170921152603&h=f203a4e5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20170921/photo/bkn-20170921111104481-0921_00822_001_04b.jpg?20170921152603\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20170921%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20170921111104481-0921_00822_001_04b.jpg%3F20170921152603&h=f6c40a38&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">發生工人墮斃的黃埔花園。(左錦鴻攝)</span><br />\n【12:25】勞工處派員到場就意外調查，警方登上大廈天台了解。<br />\n<br />\n紅磡環海街黃埔花園發生奪命工業意外，今早10時許，一名姓李(62)歲滅蟲工人，與工友在第10期綠苑第4座16樓天台，推着手推車及工具滅蟲。期間，事主被發現連同手推車和滅蟲工具從高處墮下，倒臥大廈正門對開，保安員聞巨響循聲查看，慌忙報警求助。救護員接報趕至，經檢查後證實事主當場死亡，警員用帳篷遮蓋屍體。<br />\n<br />\n警方封鎖現場，經初步調查後，相信事主在天台滅蟲時不慎失足，從沒有圍欄的天台墮下，期間砸中5樓外牆一個用作更換鋁窗的棚架，砸斷一支棚竹。<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">由於事主身上繫有安全帶，真正墮樓原因仍有待調查</span></strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/31.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，警方正聯絡其家人了解。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20170921/bkn-20170921111104481-0921_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20170921%2Fbkn-20170921111104481-0921_00822_001.html&d=GxrWmGD6ZKzW0zi6a2chVgtTNu1qqkxUxYmVHECffP4%3D&h=008e92ec\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20170921/bkn-20170921111104481-0921_00822_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"d79d2f254b743227bf6f24b5de94ab2ecb4695a3","tid":408396,"uid":26451,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-21T07:45:38.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"ab7cf198e719af2f19c209640a3bdc7682def073","tid":408396,"uid":53121,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-21T07:48:42.000Z","msg":"又係黃埔花園<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n無幾耐之前先有個阿伯抹窗失足跌死<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/24.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"915eb5d40f52fe526dafc0502a4076baaa0aeba8","tid":408396,"uid":50740,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-21T07:49:19.000Z","msg":"福氣"},{"pid":"aea62d70d2506ffde678793c0e580987c440f6da","tid":408396,"uid":10692,"like":0,"dislike":9,"score":-9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-21T07:53:24.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"a846c03c1cb47db9df8d21e3831d00cfc4372791","tid":408396,"uid":6297,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-21T08:00:10.000Z","msg":"有安全帶但係無地方扣呢"},{"pid":"83d9bb8eff69c4eef0a46b7d62798ac8874fbe44","tid":408396,"uid":68094,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-21T08:00:31.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"a0e1ce494d0639a9c68e8ce18097022064d0af8e","tid":408396,"uid":24270,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-21T08:24:38.000Z","msg":"扣返落自己身度"},{"pid":"a9ef8edac5d8cc39de5db41239e893ca71215c97","tid":408396,"uid":30182,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-21T08:27:43.000Z","msg":"又黃埔<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/31.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/31.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aa8c0ab62c667498813f8018081aaa5e45972321","tid":408396,"uid":30972,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-21T08:36:23.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>扣返落自己身度</blockquote><br />\n好多工人都會咁其實<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"da8f677485881001036af56b79de9b6c25917e18","tid":408396,"uid":34410,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy